---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy">
  <Header />

  <main class="py-8">
    <HeroSection 
      title="Cookie Policy" 
      description="Learn about the cookies used on Green Orbit Digital, how they work, and how to manage your preferences."
    />

    <section class="py-12 bg-white dark:bg-secondary-500">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 space-y-6">

        <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> August 25, 2025</p>
        <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> August 25, 2025</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">What are cookies?</h2>
        <p>
          Cookies are small text files stored on your device when a website loads. They help ensure proper website function, enhance security, improve user experience, and analyse performance to identify areas for improvement.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">How do we use cookies?</h2>
        <p>
          Our website uses both first-party and third-party cookies. First-party cookies are essential for site functionality and do not collect personally identifiable data. Third-party cookies help us monitor performance, track interaction, secure services, deliver relevant content, and enhance user experience.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Types of cookies we use</h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Necessary</h3>
        <p>
          Necessary cookies enable basic site features like secure login and consent preferences. They do not store personally identifiable data.
        </p>

        <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700">
              <th class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-left">Cookie</th>
              <th class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-left">Duration</th>
              <th class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-left">Description</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">cookieyes-consent</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">1 year</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">Remembers users' consent preferences; no personal information stored.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">__cf_bm</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">1 hour</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">Cloudflare Bot Management support.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">_GRECAPTCHA</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">6 months</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">Google Recaptcha bot identification.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">_cfuvid</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">session</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">Calendly session tracking for consistent experience.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">rc::a, rc::b, rc::c, rc::f</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">session / never expires</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">Google Recaptcha bot detection.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">m</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">1 year 1 month 4 days</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">Stripe fraud prevention.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">__stripe_mid</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">1 year</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">Stripe unique session identifier.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">__stripe_sid</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">1 hour</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">Stripe session identifier for single session.</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Manage cookie preferences</h2>
        <p>
          You can modify your cookie settings anytime via the <strong>Consent Preferences</strong> button above. You may revisit the cookie banner, update your preferences, or withdraw consent immediately.
        </p>
        <p>
          Browsers also provide ways to block or delete cookies. For guidance:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Chrome:</strong> <a href="https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/32050" target="_blank">https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/32050</a></li>
          <li><strong>Safari:</strong> <a href="https://support.apple.com/en-in/guide/safari/sfri11471/mac" target="_blank">https://support.apple.com/en-in/guide/safari/sfri11471/mac</a></li>
          <li><strong>Firefox:</strong> <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/clear-cookies-and-site-data-firefox?redirectslug=delete-cookies-remove-info-websites-stored&redirectlocale=en-US" target="_blank">https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/clear-cookies-and-site-data-firefox</a></li>
          <li><strong>Internet Explorer:</strong> <a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/topic/how-to-delete-cookie-files-in-internet-explorer-bca9446f-d873-78de-77ba-d42645fa52fc" target="_blank">https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/topic/how-to-delete-cookie-files-in-internet-explorer-bca9446f-d873-78de-77ba-d42645fa52fc</a></li>
        </ul>

        <p>If you use a different browser, refer to its official support documentation.</p>

        <p><em>Cookie Policy generated by CookieYes - Cookie Policy Generator</em></p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>